		</Row>

		<Row Tag="LOC_TRADITION_STATO_DEL_MAR_MARINE_PRODUCTION_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>+2 [icon:YIELD_PRODUCTION] Production for each Marine tile.</Text>
		</Row>

		<!--Venice Unique Traditions-->
		<Row Tag="LOC_TRADITION_LAGUNA_PROTETTA_NAME">
			<Text>Laguna Protetta</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_TRADITION_LAGUNA_PROTETTA_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Coastal Settlements receive +3 [icon:YIELD_CULTURE] Culture.</Text>
		</Row>

		<Row Tag="LOC_TRADITION_FORNA_DE_MURANO_NAME">
			<Text>Fornace di Murano</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_TRADITION_FORNA_DE_MURANO_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Urban Center buildings receive +2 [icon:YIELD_GOLD] Gold.</Text>
		</Row>

		<Row Tag="LOC_TRADITION_COSTRUZIONE_NAVALE_ACCELERATA_NAME">
			<Text>Costruzione Navale Accellerata</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_TRADITION_COSTRUZIONE_NAVALE_ACCELERATA_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>+50%[icon:YIELD_GOLD] Gold towards purchasing Urban Center Buildings.</Text>
		</Row>

		<Row Tag="LOC_TRADITION_POTENZIA_VENEZIA_NAME">
			<Text>Potenza di Venezia</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_TRADITION_POTENZIA_VENEZIA_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Whenever you build a Naval Combat Unit, the city you built it in gains 25% of its cost as [icon:YIELD_GOLD] Gold.</Text>
		</Row>
